member.remarks:
Example:

options.HandleExceptionsUsing = (exception, context) =>
{
    var inertia = context.RequestServices.GetRequiredService<IInertiaService>();
    return inertia.Render("Error", new { message = exception.Message });
};

Register in the pipeline for specific routes:

app.MapGet("/dashboard", handler).AddEndpointFilter<EncryptHistoryEndpointFilter>();
// or for MVC:
[EncryptHistory]
public IActionResult Dashboard() => ...

The simplest use is to add it as route-specific middleware:

app.Map("/secure", secure =>
{
    secure.UseMiddleware<EncryptHistoryMiddleware>();
    secure.Run(handler);
});
